!.env.example

## 🔥 Firebase
.firebase/
firebase-debug.log
firestore-debug.log
ui-debug.log

## ☁️ Deployment / Hosting
.vercel/
.netlify/
.wrangler/
Dockerfile.prod
docker-compose.override.yml

## 🔒 Security & DB
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
.sentryclirc

## 🏠 Local Dev
.local/
local/

# --- 6. Testing & Coverage ---
## 🧪 Testing & Coverage
coverage/
*.lcov
.nyc_output/
test-results/
playwright-report/
playwright/.cache/
.auth/
.vscode-test/

