# --- 8. Global Allow-List (Exceptions) ---
#
# This section MUST be at the end.
# It overrides general rules from above to
# allow specific, shared config files.
#
## ✅ VS Code Team Settings
# Ignore all of .vscode, *except* for these specific files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/cspell.json


.moon/cache
**/script-config.production.ts
**/script-config.staging.ts


script-config.*.ts
test-results/

*.gd.uid
examples
